description: Potash America, Inc., an exploration stage company, focuses on the development of fertilizer and agri-business assets in Canada. It intends to acquire and develop potash, montmorillonite, bentonite, and gypsum assets into agri-products. The company was formerly known as Adtomize Inc. and changed its name to Potash America, Inc. in March 2011. Potash America, Inc. was founded in 2007 and is based in Boca Raton, Florida.
